1190.name: Dur Mn14
1190.Applications: This electrode with a recovery of 140% can be used forjoining and overlay on manganese steels that are worn out and need to be rebuild. Heat input should be low.
1190.Suitable_For: austenitic manganese steel, high impact loads, hammers, crushers, rebuilding, hardfacing, rails, crossings, Breaker teeth, etc..
